title: CZW Cage of Death
data: 2 Girls , 1 Cup ( Beef Wellington and Greg Excellent ) and L.J . Cruz defeated GNC ( Alex Colon and Joe Gacy ) and Nicky Benz
The H8 Club ( Nick Gage and Justice Pain and Nate Hatred ) defeated The Miracle Ultraviolence Connection ( Brodie Lee , Cheech and Cloudy )
Singles match for the CZW World Junior Heavyweight Championship
Danny Demanto and Jon Dahmer defeated Derek Frazier and Niles Young ( c )
Tag team match for the CZW World Tag Team Championship
Nick Gage defeated The Messiah and Ruckus ( c )
Three-way dance for the CZW World Heavyweight Championship
WHACKS defeated SeXXXy Eddy and Viking
Team CZW ( Danny Havoc , Drake Younger , Necro Butcher and Toby Klein ) ( with Halfbreed Billy Gram ) defeated Team MBA ( Brain Damage , DJ Hyde , Dustin Lee and Scotty Vortekz )
section_text: Cage of Death IXPromotionCombat Zone Wrestling [ 11 ] DateDecember 8 , 2007 [ 10 ] CityPhiladelphia , Pennsylvania [ 11 ] VenueViking Hall [ 11 ] Event chronology ← PreviousNight of Infamy 6 Next →New Year 's Resolutions Cage of Death IX was the ninth annual Cage of Death event produced by the Combat Zone Wrestling professional wrestling promotion . It took place on December 8 , 2007 , at the CZW Arena in Philadelphia , Pennsylvania . The event was the seventh consecutive Cage of Death at the CZW Arena . [ 11 ]
